  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Wow, you're fast! That's awesome. We'll head straight to the next quest. It's important to know your limits, but it's also important to test your abilities. Want to try defeating some powerful monsters?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This time, you'll be hunting #r#o9##k, which you WON'T find just casually wandering around. You'll have to go into every portal to find them. I want you to defeat #r1#k! "
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Also, I've heard that #b#p12##k is collecting something from the #r#o9#s#k... If you haven't filled #b#p12##k's request yet, you might want to try doing so while you train."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If it seems too difficult for you, come back after training against easier monsters. "
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So you've taken care of the #r#o9##k? Weren't they hard to find? Let's see how strong you have become..."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Great job! You're now strong enough to hold your own against any monster here. You'll have to start making job decisions once you reach level 10. If you haven’t met #p19# from #m1010# yet, you should go see her. She’ll give you a lot of information while presenting you with various challenges. If we meet again someday, let’s catch up. Goodbye!"
        }
      },
